sequenceDiagram
    participant O as 编排控制
    participant T as 工具运行时
    participant G as 治理层
    participant E as 外部系统
    O->>T: Validated ActionIntent + step context
    T->>T: Prepare: contract / args / call_id
    T->>G: Authorize(subject, action, resource, digest)
    alt deny 或需审批
        G-->>T: deny / require_approval
        T-->>O: Typed policy observation
    else allow
        G-->>T: allow + decision_ref
        T->>E: Dispatch(deadline, idempotency_key)
        alt 收到响应
            E-->>T: result / typed error
            T->>T: Observe + validate + redact
        else 派发后超时
            T->>T: unknown_outcome
        end
        T->>T: Commit call record / effect receipt
        T-->>O: Typed Observation
    end
